(25, 13, 1, 'Các năm trước', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://www.phys.hcmus.edu.vn/vi/index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=423:l-i-c-m-on-t-ban-t-ch-c-ngay-truy-n-th-ng-khoa&amp;catid=13:tin-cho-cb-vc-khoa&amp;Itemid=233\"><span style=\"color:#0000cc\">LỜI CẢM ƠN TỪ BAN TỔ CHỨC NG&Agrave;Y TRUYỀN THỐNG KHOA</span></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://www.phys.hcmus.edu.vn/vi/index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=651&amp;catid=26\" title=\"Ngày Hội Truyền Thống Khoa 2016\"><span style=\"color:#0000cc\">DANH S&Aacute;CH Đ&Oacute;NG G&Oacute;P V&Agrave; B&Aacute;O C&Aacute;O THU CHI NG&Agrave;Y TRUYỀN THỐNG KHOA 2016</span></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://www.phys.hcmus.edu.vn/vi/index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=422:bao-cao-thu-chi-va-danh-sach-dong-gop-ngay-truy-n-th-ng-khoa&amp;catid=19:tin-sinh-vien&amp;Itemid=197\" title=\"\"><span style=\"color:#0000cc\">DANH S&Aacute;CH Đ&Oacute;NG G&Oacute;P V&Agrave; B&Aacute;O C&Aacute;O THU CHI NG&Agrave;Y TRUYỀN THỐNG KHOA 2014</span></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\">ẢNH NG&Agrave;Y TRUYỀN THỐNG KHOA QUA C&Aacute;C NĂM</span></strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>..............................................................................................................</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>2001</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><embed height=\"400\" pluginspage=\"http://www.macromedia.com/go/getflashplayer\" src=\"https://static.googleusercontent.com/external_content/picasaweb.googleusercontent.com/slideshow.swf\" type=\"application/x-shockwave-flash\" width=\"600\"></embed></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>2002</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><embed height=\"400\" pluginspage=\"http://www.macromedia.com/go/getflashplayer\" src=\"https://static.googleusercontent.com/external_content/picasaweb.googleusercontent.com/slideshow.swf\" type=\"application/x-shockwave-flash\" widt