ohm</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>University of Stockholm, Sweden</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Sweden</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Executive Committee</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>11</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Prof. MasaharuNomachi</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Osaka University, Japan</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Japan</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Executive Committee</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', 'Thông tin về lớp học quốc tế chuyên đề các hệ thống thời gian thực-The International Real Time School 2016'),
(424, 226, 2, 'Information about international class specializing in real-time systems-The International Real Time School 2016', '<p>Experimental practice is very important for students. Therefore, from July 18 to 26, the nuclear engineering laboratory - Ho Chi Minh City University of Natural Sciences in collaboration with the IEEE Nuclear Physics and Nuclear Physics Research Association (IEEE NPSS), Research Center Osaka Nuclear Physics University (RCNP) organizes the International Class on Real-Time Systems at Linh Trung Base Nuclear Technology Laboratory. The class not only provides students and students with lectures but also provides laboratory exercises. Lectures and exercises are conducted by experts in the field of radiation recording, providing learners with the latest updated knowledge. For more information about classes, please visit the Nuclear Engineering Laboratory web site:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>http://ntlab.hcmus.edu.vn/en/rt2016-school/</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The goal of the class is:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Training young scientists in the field of radiation recording and its application.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Stimulate the development of real-time systems in Southeast Asia.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Promote young scientists to participate in the field of radiation measurement as well as related fields.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Participants:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Classes are for students and graduate students.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Information about the curriculum and list of classes here.</p>\r\n\r\n<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"width:653px\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Num.</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Full name</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Institution</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Nationality</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Note</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>1</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Prof. Chau Van