INSERT INTO `posts_lang` (`id`, `post_id`, `lang_id`, `title`, `content`, `excerpt`) VALUES
(460, 248, 2, 'WELCOME TO WELCOME THE DAY OF VIETNAMESE TEACHERS WITH THE FAMILY PHYSICS PHYSICS AND GIVE 21 SCHOLARSHIPS FROM THE VLTH SUPPORT FUND', '<p>&ldquo;Teachers raise books to lead them</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Teach people to help their country &rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Teachers, ferry drivers bringing generations of students to the shore of knowledge. In recognition of that great and sacred teaching, every year, the whole country immerses itself in the jubilant atmosphere of Vietnam Teachers&#39; Day November 20, a lifelong tradition for pupils and students to Send flowers to her teachers the most beautiful bouquet with deepest gratitude. Recently, on the morning of November 18, 2018, the Department of Informatics Physics at the University of Natural Sciences was pleased to welcome retired teachers, visiting lecturers and all the lecturers of the Department, especially including Assoc. Dang Van Liet, former head of the Physics Department, former head of the Department of Physics and Informatics, attended the gratitude ceremony for teachers.</p>\r\n\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.phys.hcmus.edu.vn/vlth/images/DSCF0302.jpg\" style=\"height:376px; width:580px\" /></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.phys.hcmus.edu.vn/vlth/images/DSCF0420.jpg\" style=\"height:387px; width:580px\" /></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td colspan=\"2\">The ceremony took place in a solemn and warm atmosphere with the presence of teachers and students at the Department of Informatics Physics.</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p>The ceremony took place solemnly, warmly and also very emotionally.This is an opportunity not only for students studying at the Department but also a lot of alumni returning to visit, send greetings and give flowers to teachers to show their gratitude to the boatmen who have guided, dedicated, loved and taught the people. At the ceremony, students also had the opportunity to interact with alumni, and to listen to advice, share about their real experiences, or words of encouragement to help them be more motivated in learning, more stable in their academic career.</p>\r\n\r\n<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.phys.hcmus.edu.vn/vlth/images/DSCF0343.jpg\" style=\"height:387px; width:580px\" /></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.phys.hcmus.edu.vn/vlth/images/DSCF0340.jpg\" style=\"height:356px; width:580px\" /></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td colspan=\"2\">Informatics Physics Physics teachers give scholarships to students to support them in their learning process.</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p>Learning has always been a long and difficult process. Every student, student coming to the path of education is a different story and circumstance: &ldquo;I decided to think about extra tutoring to ensure the best learning ... so far the amount of money saved is gradually exhausted. but the project is more and more and is going to graduate project &rdquo;,&ldquo; My family has a lot of financial difficulties and an additional burden from money for me to go to school &rdquo;,&ldquo; I just hope to receive support Partly to make my life less difficult, I am very happy and happy. &quot;&quot; Receiving a scholarship from the subject will be a valuable resource to help me achieve my academic goals. &quot; Listening to the sharing of students studying at the Department, VLTH Scholarship Support Fund has brought 21 scholarships, each worth VND 2,000,000. The scholarship value is not great, but these are spiritual gifts to encourage students to study well.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>VLTH Scholarship Fund comes from the desire to sponsor some scholarships of Mr. Nguyen Xuan Huy&#39;s family and also from the opinion of many of the Department&#39;s alumni who want to help students currently studying at Department of Informatics Physics. And the Department has set up this scholarship fund to support and encourage the students of VLTH with difficult family circumstances or students with good academic achievements.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"width:599px\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td colspan=\"4\"><strong>REPORT ON SUPPLY OF COMPUTER PHYSICS SCHOLARSHIP</strong></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td colspan=\"4\">(t&iacute;nh đến 11/2018)</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>STT</strong></td>\r\n			<td colspan=\"2\"><strong>CATEGORY</strong></td>\r\n			<td><strong>Amount (VND)</strong></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>I</strong></td>\r\n			<td><strong>NĂM 2015</strong></td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>1</td>\r\n			<td>Thu&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>39,080,000</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>2</td>\r\n			<td>Chi (18 suất x 1.500.000đ)</td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>27,000,000</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>3</td>\r\n			<td colspan=\"2\">Tồn quỹ năm 2015</td>\r\n			<td>12,080,000</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>II</strong></td>\r\n			<td><strong>NĂM 2016</strong></td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>1</td>\r\n			<td>Thu&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>31,900,000</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>2</td>\r\n			<td>Chi (15 suất x 2.000.000đ)</td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>30,000,000</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>3</td>\r\n			<td colspan=\"2\">Tồn quỹ năm 2016</td>\r\n			<td>1,900,000</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>III</strong></td>\r\n			<td><strong>NĂM 2017</strong></td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>1</td>\r\n			<td>Thu&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>38,600,000</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r