INSERT INTO `posts_lang` (`id`, `post_id`, `lang_id`, `title`, `content`, `excerpt`) VALUES
(478, 257, 2, 'Celebrating Vietnam Teachers\' Day 2019', '<p><em><strong>CELEBRATE VIETNAM TEACHERS DAY 2019</strong></em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em><strong>Department of Computer Science brilliant colors and<br />\r\ndeep gratitude to the teachers</strong></em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>&ldquo;Back to the old school with memories. The shadow of the teacher still does not leave. &rdquo;</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>November - the most beautiful time of the year, of meetings, gatherings, is a month of deep gratitude to the teachers who always light the lamp of knowledge for generations birth, student. In order to continue the good tradition of the &quot;Great Guru&quot; of the Vietnamese people, recently, on the morning of November 17, 1919, the Department of Physics and Informatics, University of Natural Sciences honored to welcome retired teachers. , visiting lecturers and all lecturers of the Department, especially Assoc. Dang Van Liet, former head of the Department of Physics, former head of the Department of Informatics Physics attended the gratitude ceremony for teachers.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.phys.hcmus.edu.vn/vlth/images/H1.jpg\" /></td>\r\n			<td><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.phys.hcmus.edu.vn/vlth/images/H2.jpg\" /></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.phys.hcmus.edu.vn/vlth/images/H3.jpg\" /></td>\r\n			<td><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.phys.hcmus.edu.vn/vlth/images/H4.jpg\" /></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p><em>The ceremony took place in a solemn, warm atmosphere with the presence of teachers and students at the Department<br />\r\nComputational Physics</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>In the solemn and warm atmosphere of the ceremony, fresh bouquets of flowers and good wishes from alumni as well as students studying at the Department were sent to the teachers every day. still plying the lesson plans, always dedicated, loving, raising students&#39; wings to a bright future. This is also a traditional gathering, a meeting, a talk and a share of experiences and encouragement from alumni to the next generation with the hope that they will always believe and try. Make more efforts on your path of education.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&quot;Education has bitter roots but sweet fruits.&quot; This past career has always been an arduous and difficult journey. Understanding the concerns as well as listening to the thoughts and aspirations of students studying at the Department, at the ceremony, the VLTH Scholarship Fund has brought 14 scholarships, each worth 2,500,000 VND copper. The scholarship value is not great, but these are spiritual gifts to encourage students to study well.</p>\r\n\r\n<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.phys.hcmus.edu.vn/vlth/images/H5.jpg\" /></td>\r\n			<td><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.phys.hcmus.edu.vn/vlth/images/H6.jpg\" /></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Informatics Physics Physics teachers give scholarships to students to support them in their learning process.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>VLTH Scholarship Fund comes from the desire to sponsor some scholarships of Mr. Nguyen Xuan Huy&#39;s family and also from the opinion of many of the Department&#39;s alumni who want to help students currently studying at Department of Informatics Physics. And the Department has set up this scholarship fund to support and encourage VLTH students with difficult family circumstances or students with good academic results.</p>\r\n\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"width:599px\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td colspan=\"4\"><strong>B&Aacute;O C&Aacute;O TỒN QUỸ HỌC BỔNG VẬT L&Yacute; TIN HỌC&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp